      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RAPID LULU (6) continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at her last four runs. Last start finished 3rd over 390m at this track beaten 3.5 lengths (22.32) behind Fun Day in a Mix 5 on July 17. Yet to score from this box but has never missed the frame in two starts. Deserves a win and gets her chance. IT'S THE ZIGGY (1) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fifth (20.16) in a Mix 5 at this track. Expected to give a good account. COALMAN JACK (2) had a tricky draw last time and although midfield in fourth wasn't far away finishing 3 lengths from the winner (20.03). Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings four times from seven attempts. Expected to feature in the finish. HAMISO (5) is one of the chances after a surprise minor prize last time.",
